org.miloss.fgsms.presentation

Class ProxyLoader

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.miloss.fgsms.presentation.ProxyLoader
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IProxyLoader

    public class ProxyLoader
extends Object
implements IProxyLoader
    Loads client proxy objects for the fgsms Web services using the configuration file settings. This class will use the current thread's context class loader to attempt to determine if we are running in a CXF or JbossWS-Native environment. If it cannot be determined, an exception is thrown. This class is similar to the factory pattern, however it is not explicitly configurable
    Since:
    6.2
    Author:
    AO
